text: Alix of France (July/August 1150 - 1197/1198) was the youngest daughter of Louis VII of France and Eleanor of Aquitaine. She was married to Theobald V of Blois in 1164. Their children included: *Louis I of Blois *Margaret of Blois Category:French royalty Category:1151 births Category:1190s deaths
